column5: What are you contacting us about?

column6:
Hello,
My name is Vinay Kumar Sadhwani.I am currently a freshman at Northeastern University. I wanted to know more about IDEA and wanted to be a part of it. I would want to meet with one of the faculty members of IDEA.Please can you set up a time for me to meet a faculty member to discuss on how I can improve my skills.

Thank You.

Regards,
Vinay Kumar Sadhwani
